title: Penn and Teller: Bullshit! (Gun Control Episode)
description:
I was a bit disappointed to see this torrent from another user die, so I feel obligated to bring it back over here.  


Approximately 30 minutes long, this documentary talks about our Second Amendment, and interviews those who both support it and those who do not.  This documentary is incredibly pro-gun, and there are many excellent points said in here.  An outstanding video to watch, and very much worth watching for those who like to debate. :)
